      • select

        public K select(int rank)
        Return the K in the symbol table of a given rank. This K has the property that there are rank Ks in the symbol table that are smaller. In other words, this K is the (rank+1)st smallest K in the symbol table.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        the K in the symbol table of given rank
